tafsir[25]{c,v,t}:
  20,13,"Min Mi Suﾉ妬ke ma -an Muusaa- fii yottinngol Nulal an ngal, heﾉ熔 ko Mi woni Wahayinnde kon e maaﾉ預."
  20,14,"Pellet, ko Min woni Alla reweteeﾉ熔 e goonga alaa tanaa Am, Rewam Min Tun tottir Julde nden e noone ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 timmude fii yo a annditam e nder mayre."
  20,15,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko arayngal feere alaa ngal hewtay, Miﾉ熔 ﾉ預ﾉ殿 suuﾉ蓉de ngal Tagaaﾉ熔 woo anndaa nde ngal waﾉ預ta, kono hiﾉ兎 anndira maa- ndeeji maggal sabu ko Nulaaﾉ熔 on humpitiﾉ兎 kon; fii yo yoﾉ兎 kala wonkii ko ki golli kon, si tawii ko ko moﾆｴﾆｴi maaﾉ蓉m si ko ko bone."
  20,16,"Wata martine(firlitma) e goonginngol ngal e heblanorgol golle moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n, on mo gomﾉ擁naa ngal immorde e yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, o jokki ko welata wonkii makko kin immorde e harminaaﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, o halkori sabu ﾉ蓉m."
  20,17,"Ko woni nden huunde wonunde ka ﾃｱaamo maaﾉ預 an Muusaa?"
  20,18,"Muusaa (yo o his) maaki: ""Ndun ko tuggordu am; miﾉ熔 tuggoo ndu ka yaadu, miﾉ熔 woppira ndu leﾉ遼容 ﾉ容n fii yo kaaki majje ﾉ擁n saaman dammi am ﾉ擁n, miﾉ熔 mari nafa kadi e mayru hara wanaa koo ko mi jaﾅ逆ii""."
  20,19,"Alla Daali: ""Liﾉ砥 ndu, an Muusaa""."
  20,20,"Muusaa liﾉ妬 ndu, ndu waylii mboddi hindi yaha e yaccaade."
  20,21,"Alla Daalani Muusaa (yo o his): ""nanngu tuggordu ndun, wota a hulu immorde e waylagol mayru mboddi, aray Men rutta ndu si nanngii ndu faade e noone mayru arano on."
  20,22,"Waﾉ蓉 junngo maaﾉ預 ngon ka nder jiiba maa; ngo yaltay ko ngo rawnungo hara ngo colﾉ預a(ngo wonddani e baras), ﾉ蓉m ko maande ﾉ擁ﾉ預ﾉ兎re maaﾉ預."
  20,23,"Men hollii ma ﾉ擁i maandeeji ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 fii yo Men holle -an Muusaa- immorde e Aayeeje Amen Mawﾉ容 tinndinﾉ容 ﾉ容n e Kattanﾉ容 Amen, e wonndema kadi an ko o Nulaaﾉ熔 immorde ka Alla."
  20,24,"Yahu -an Muusaa- ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o yawtii keerol ngol e keeferaaku ngun e sanndalﾉ預nagol Alla."
  20,25,"Muusaa (yo o his) maaki: ""Jooma, yaajinanam ﾉ兎rnde am nden; fii yo mi waawu ronnditaade larraaji(lorooji) ﾉ擁n."
  20,26,"Newinanaa mi fiyaake am on."
  20,27,"Wawnaa lam yewtugol yewtere laaﾉ砥nde."
  20,28,"Fii yo ﾉ殿 faamu haala am kan si Nulal am ngal yottike e maﾉ橡兎."
  20,29,"Waﾉ預naa mi walloowo jeyaaﾉ熔 ka ﾉ兎ynguure am o walla lam e fiyakuuji am."
  20,30,"Haaruuna geﾉ預l Imraana ko musiﾉ遼熔 am."
  20,31,"Semmbiniraa mo keeci am."
  20,32,"Waﾉ蓉 mo kafidaaﾉ熔 e am e nder Nulal ngal."
  20,33,"Fii yo men Senine Seninaali heewuﾉ擁."
  20,34,"Men jaﾅ逆oMaa jaﾅ逆a heewuﾉ熔."
  20,35,"Pellet, An A Laatike Humpitiiﾉ熔 fii amen, huunde suuﾉ預naaki Ma e fiyaake amen."
  20,36,"Alla Daali: ""Gomﾉ擁i Men okkii ma ko ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥ﾉ預a kon an Muusaa""."
  20,37,"Gomﾉ擁i Men Neeminiino e maaﾉ預 e laawol goo."
